{"tid":30341,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"【無知一問】有關a7ii用slog影相","createTime":"2016-12-09T06:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T06:19:11.000Z","uid":5469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b2f57c23e94657e191dceb5c5d7baf1b598782e","tid":30341,"uid":5469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"小弟試用a7ii 個 slog pp7 影RAW<br />\n發現佢將光暗低compress 左<br />\n當我放入Lightroom 發現執出來好似有小小唔同<br />\n<br />\n上網睇係方便拍片人執片用，可以保留多啲細節<br />\n想問下其實咁影同原來張RAW保留嘅細節有無分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1935b0b76ece7bba609fdd2e361b79cb774b91","tid":30341,"uid":5469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ace0db0a4850e18e285c883fb3cce92a5a4c46","tid":30341,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:12:46.000Z","msg":"影相有RAW<br />\n部機可以capture到又decode到既訊息已經係哂張RAW度<br />\n你打slog落去只係幫你拉平條curve再flat d<br />\n你自己用RAW拉都係一樣<br />\n唔使專登又SLOG一次<br />\n<br />\n拍片唔打SLOG既話就等如你影jpeg，好多光暗位會好難救，所以先要用SLOG有咁flat得咁flat"},{"pid":"56bb8aaf50ee38b2fc955d6adbb4554b3816adb7","tid":30341,"uid":8909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:19:11.000Z","msg":"其實唔係好明點樣slog 影raw"}]}